name: Da Varanda #004
description: 1 week, an apartment balcony and a camera. This series of photos is being produced from the balcony of my apartment. For 1 week, I will photograph the life that I can see from up here on the 10th floor. This is the fourth photo, size 2968 x 1974 px - ISO 400 | 66mm | f/6,3 | 8 sec. All will be minted in 100 editions at a low price and after the sale period, those that are not sold will be burned.
